long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Elevate your browsing experience with the "Floating Cubes Dashboard" extension. Featuring a stunning background of transparent cubes floating over a lush green field bathed in soft light, this extension combines style and functionality.

Key Features:
- Custom Shortcuts
- Real-Time Clock
- News
- Live Weather Updates
